abstract: TITUSVILLE, Penn., April 30.--The April oil report, to be published to-morrow, will somewhat disappoint those expecting a bullish record. abstract: NIAGARA FALLS, Ontario, May 30.-- Thomas Little, alias Watson, a noted criminal, was arrested last night near the International Bridge by Detectives Youing and McMicken, of Ontario, and lodged an jail here. Little is wanted in Toronto for shooting Constable Armstrong some time ago, while the latter was attempting to arrest him. He is also wanted in several other places in Canada and the States for various crimes.
